What this app does
KB DocBot watches recently merged product PRs in smth-payments, asks an OpenAI agent whether customer-facing docs need to change, reads the current docs from smth-docs, and if needed opens a PR in smth-docs with the suggested updates.

The flow is:

Fetch merged PRs from the product repo.
Send those PRs to the agent.
Fetch relevant help docs from the docs repo.
Decide whether docs should change.
If needed, create a branch, update Markdown files, and open a docs PR.
